type: TS LF Trading Bot Error - Snapshot Instruction Evaluation Error

definition.text: This error occured while evaluating an instruction as part of the process of generating a Snapshot. This did not prevent the Snapshot from being created, but the value for the particular instruction was set to zero.

paragraphs.text: In the following section, you will find the information recorded when the error occurred.
